{
  "stem": "14552.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And all those people who were there in the rooms and who could hardly get out of bed, they were all in the-- and the doctors and everyone was running after me.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I am screaming.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[CRYING] [SOBBING] And there, by the front steps is my brother.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well-- and he was always my best friend.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was my protector always.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When somebody-- when I would walk with the-- not very straight, he would say straighten out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Eat like this.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Don't do that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he would always make sure-- very gently.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He was-- very gently.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he was there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "My friend, my brother.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Well, [SOBBING] that reunion was very, very special.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I'll be looking for more and looking and looking.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then this brother who had-- his lungs were very badly affected.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he got into a-- another hospital by the yacht club in Prague.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There's only one yacht club there at that time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he got into that hospital.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And eventually, I was transferred out of that hospital and went where my brother was.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And, and we were together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And my sister, then, she was discharged.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And she took a job with someone.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And then she came to visit us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So now we are the three of us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we cannot find anybody in there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was a very anxious time to see who knows whom-- looking for whom.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then my sister goes home to Munkacs to see if she can find my brother.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she finds him, but he cannot come out because he has typhoid.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, the fever.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He has-- he wasn't able to move.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And here I am in the Prague.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I'm-- I have-- I need somebody to take care of me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I'm young, and she is in charge of me.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
